		{"id":"129acb6b79d57927","type":"text","text":"# APC\n\n## 自動調整設備的參數\n\n# 會透過 演算法 來調整Recipe\n\n## 會先向RMS與Dimension要資料回來計算\n\n## 有兩個transaction 代表 APC回傳給EAP, EAP向APC詢問\n\n![[Pasted image 20240528165406.png]]","x":9800,"y":-2016,"width":639,"height":235,"color":"4"},
